Features of Grafana:
Open source
Visualization using dynamic dashboard and filtering
Create alerts when threshold crosses
Explore Metrics and Logs
Supports all DB
Create multiple Panels which retrieves data from multiple sources (InfluxDB, Oracle, MySQL)

Flow of Grafana:
Telegraf (Script or Agent which Collects System Data i.e. OSMetrics from Server ) -> InfluxDB (Data Source) -> Grafana (Visualise Data)

